k
N(k)
S(k)
k\ge 1
s_i=(k+1)!+i!
i=1,\dots,k
N(k)=\sum_{i=1}^k s_i
S(k)=\{s_i:1\le i\le k\}
\sum_{i=1}^k i!<(k+1)!
(k-1)s_k<N_k<(k+1)s_1
N(k)=a_1+a_2+\dots+a_n
a_i\in S(k)
1\le i\le n
ns_1\le N(k)\le ns_k
k=n
M(k)=N(k)-k(k+1)!
b_i=a_i-(k+1)!
M(k)=\sum_{i=1}^k i!=\sum_{i=1}^k b_i
b_i\in\{i!:1\le i\le k\}
